##A nurse in the Intensive Care Unit in Hubei Province: quietly "strong"

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Zhu junyu, ICU nurse, Department of anesthesiology, Hebei Medical University

Lu Xinwen, reporter, thepaper.cn

February 21, the eighth batch of Hebei Province to Hubei Medical Team 175 people set foot on the journey, to this point, Hebei sent a total of 1036 medical personnel to Hubei.

With the outbreak of new crown pneumonia, we had a mixed Spring Festival. For more than 20 days, the mood of ordinary people rose and fell with the epidemic, until recently, there was good news -- More people were discharged than were diagnosed. At a time when everyone was relieved, there were countless medical staff who stood by silently for the final victory, especially those in the intensive care unit, who did not dare to relax, as they have every moment and every day of their professional lives, but there are some different, because they know that now they are guarding a precious life, is a family's future, but also the National People's sense of security.

Among them was Liu Yexing, an anesthesiologist at the Hebei Medical University, who had been in Wuhan for more than 20 days and had been staying at the intensive-care unit.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Photo courtesy of the respondents

Liu Ye Xing is in January 26 after the night shift was urgently deployed to Wuhan, in the face of various uncertainties, he said his heart will panic, but he said: "people, always have some feelings and beliefs. "

To Wuhan, in the face of the lack of protective materials, the complex medical environment, the arduous task, he first expressed that he saw Wuhan colleagues "fearless, brave, friendly" and the care of colleagues in Hebei.

Wuhan's Intensive Care Unit, because it can not turn on air conditioning, with the medical staff described as "ice and fire two days. ". As a result of wearing a closed protective clothing, mask wearing close, critical patients because of treatment needs, are prone position, need to move the patient often, every time hard operation, medical staff have the feeling of Hypoxia Asphyxia. Often is moves the patient after a body sweat, is blown by the cool wind is full of ice-cold, always worried will catch a cold.

In order to save protective clothing, work for six hours can not eat, can not drink water, coupled with the work of great intensity, often hungry to unconscious. Low blood sugar at first, in order to prevent the occurrence of low blood sugar, they need to overcome the food taste before going to work, even if too spicy dishes hard to eat, eat only white rice, but also try to eat more and more. All this pain, it takes willpower to overcome. Even so, Ye Xing said: the symptoms of severe patients improve after tracheal extubation, because the sedative used during intubation needs a period of time to metabolize, the patient will appear delirious state, Ye Xing said at this time the patient is extremely manic, will greet the medical staff of the "ancestors of the eight generations" , will pull out their own indwelling needle, or even to tear the medical staff mask, protective clothing, on the one hand will hurt patients themselves, will also give medical staff the risk of occupational exposure. There are many risks involved in caring for such patients. But Ye Xing thinks, "the patient is too pitiable, I must give them the best condition, help them hard" .

Despite all that he has done, despite all the responsibilities that ordinary people can not imagine and can hardly bear, despite all the willpower he has to keep going every day, twinkle stars doesn't feel like a hero, he said:

In this battlefield without gunpowder smoke, in the front position closest to life and death, how many white-clad soldiers like Liu ye-xing are "quietly excellent, quietly strong" , their wish may be the same as twinkle: "to travel with their families after the epidemic, breathe the air without a mask" .

Countless stars are ordinary, but also extraordinary, the most ordinary and touching!

This issue is edited by Xing Tan
